                        "value": "This collection has been arranged into two series reflecting the different types of documents in the collection, Silverman's research photocopies and Silverman's research notes.  The two series are \u003cspan class=\"ead-emph ead-emph-bold\"\u003eSeries I: Journal of Research Citations and Photocopies of Reasearch Files\u003c/span\u003e and \u003cspan class=\"ead-emph ead-emph-bold\"\u003eSeries II: Research Notes and Annotations\u003c/span\u003e."
